    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Medacta International SA</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate radiological performance of the cementless femoral
      stem AMIStem H at 1 and 5-year follow-up.

      All the patients operated at the investigational sites between April 2009 and April 2012 will
      be reviewed at 1, 5 and 10 year according to standard practice
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
